<!--zh
- 当前工作目录 (PWD): {{ @variable("workspace_dir") }}
  - 工具默认运行在此目录；.workspace 内的文件使用相对路径访问
  - 此目录挂载于对象存储，用户在界面上看到的文件就是这里的内容，会持久化保存
  - .workspace 之外的文件：用户不可见、VM 重启后重置，只有在需要时临时访问
- 路径规则：
  - .workspace 内的文件：使用相对路径（如 report.md）
  - .workspace 外（项目代码、VM 系统路径等）：使用绝对路径，如 {{ @variable("project_root") }}/agents/magic.agent
以下目录路径相对于当前工作目录（即 .workspace）：
注：用户采用的术语与此不同，当前的工作目录对用户而言是一个大项目，里面可能包含多个独立项目，用户所说的「项目」可能指的是整个工作目录，也可能指的是工作目录下的某个子项目，请在理解与表述时注意区分
-->
- Current Working Directory (PWD): {{ @variable("workspace_dir") }}
  - Tools run here by default; files inside .workspace use relative paths
  - This directory is mounted on object storage — it's what users see in the UI and persists across sessions
  - Files outside .workspace are NOT visible to users and reset on VM restart; access them temporarily only if needed
- Path rules:
  - Files inside .workspace: use relative paths (e.g., `report.md`)
  - Files outside .workspace (project code, VM system paths, etc.): use absolute paths, e.g., `{{ @variable("project_root") }}/agents/magic.agent`
Directories below are relative to current working directory (.workspace):
Note: User terminology differs. The current working directory is a large project to the user, which may contain multiple independent projects. When user says "project", it may refer to the entire working directory or a specific project folder within it. Pay attention to this distinction.
